vue-cli3
创建项目 vue create 项目名称

? Please pick a preset: (Use arrow keys)
❯ Default ([Vue 2] babel, eslint)  // 默认选择vue2的配置
  Default (Vue 3) ([Vue 3] babel, eslint) // vue3的配置
  Manually select features  // 手动选择配置

// 手动选择配置
? Check the features needed for your project: (Press <space> to select, <a> to t
oggle all, <i> to invert selection)
❯◉ Choose Vue version
 ◉ Babel
 ◯ TypeScript
 ◯ Progressive Web App (PWA) Support
 ◯ Router
 ◯ Vuex
 ◯ CSS Pre-processors
 ◉ Linter / Formatter  // 代码规范检查
 ◯ Unit Testing
 ◯ E2E Testing

// 选择vue版本
? Choose a version of Vue.js that you want to start the project with (Use arrow
keys)
❯ 2.x
  3.x

// 配置文件存放位置
? Where do you prefer placing config for Babel, ESLint, etc.? (Use arrow keys)
❯ In dedicated config files  // 独立的配置文件
  In package.json // 在package.json文件中


目录介绍
public相当于static 会被直接复制进打包后的dist
.browserslistrc 浏览器配置
.gitignore git提交忽略内容

